name: Matthew Harrison
story: Sykes grew up in a military family and always knew he wanted to serve his country. He excelled in basic training and was quickly promoted to Corporal. As a Grenadier, he has proven to be a valuable asset to his team, often being praised for his accuracy with the M320 grenade launcher. While he takes his job very seriously, he has a natural confidence and can often be found cracking jokes with his fellow squad members.
